reviewText: like the sexy playboy girls next door dvd and  any of the playboy dvds, glad I got it loved it.

If you liked Shamron Moore (Ann Marie Rozayla) in "Zombie Strippers", see her here much more lean and pre-implants. She looks hella good either way, but I prefer her in this to that. Still, I wouldn't kick her out of bed for eating crackers.

Other than Kitana, there's a nice mix of lanky girls, skinny girls and one oddly pot-bellied Eastern Bloc type near the end that was pretty hot, but not Playboy hot.

Typical Playboy nonsense.  They've got the best looking women alright. There's no doubt about it. But they don't really want to let us get to see them. It's flashes and blurring and micro-second peeks... and black&white and all the other phony artistic side of the Playboy videos.  When they somehow get it right, it's unbeatable (sorry) but don't look for it on thgis one.

this video tape is made of amateur sequences selected from thousands of tapes from girls eager to start a playboy model career.so picture quality is not always excellent,but this is highly overcomed by the quality of the models,among which the gorgeous kitana baker. Plus,the"hostess"in this 10 different playmate sequences is Deanna Brooks,a real cute one! worth the buying when you are already a fan of the playmates in question.

This may just become my favorite series from Playboy. You get more pink on this one DVD than almost all of the other Playboy DVD's combined. If you like Kitana Baker (Miller catfight girl) buy this DVD. You get both of her scenes from The Model Solution video and one from Roomates. You also see the audition tape she sent in to Playboy
